text: Jean Nako Naprapol (born 20 July 1980 in Tanna) is an international footballer for Vanuatu. He played in the 2008 and 2012 OFC Nations Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Vanuatuan footballers Category:Vanuatu international footballers Category:Association footballers not categorized by position
